# Vite client env — only variables prefixed with VITE_ are exposed to the browser.
#
# Development: copy to `.env` or `.env.local` for overrides. If unset in dev,
# the app defaults to http://localhost:8725 (see `src/config/env.ts`).
#
# Production builds: use `.env.production` — copy from `.env.production.example`
# so `vite build` / deploy inlines the deployed worker-api URL. That file is not
# loaded during `vite dev`, so local dev stays on localhost unless you override
# here.
#
# VITE_API_BASE_URL=https://your-worker-api.workers.dev
